## ğŸ“š **Daily Learning Checklist**

### **Day 1: Setup & First Component**
- [ ] Install Node.js & npm
- [ ] Create first React app
- [ ] Understand project structure
- [ ] Create functional component
- [ ] Write first JSX

### **Day 2: Components & Props**
- [ ] Create multiple components
- [ ] Pass props between components
- [ ] Destructure props
- [ ] Default props
- [ ] PropTypes

### **Day 3: State & Events**
- [ ] useState hook
- [ ] Event handlers
- [ ] Form handling
- [ ] Conditional rendering
- [ ] Lists with map()

*(Continue this pattern for 60 days)*

